	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "One of the proscribed in 43 (App. BC 4.29). Brother (see PIR(2) H 24, at end; RE 7.2513) or, more probably, father (so Syme RP 1.271) of Q. Haterius the orator, Cos. suff. In 5, whose family was senatorial (Tae. Ann. 4.61).\n" .
